<p align="center"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">English Translation</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;">By  the strength of his penance, our Ramanajua lifted and protected the  world from the destructive power of Kali.  For those who attain him, the  radiance of knowledge, proper understanding, tolerance, ability, fame,  wealth, -all these will come of their own accord.</span></p>
